[*] --> Rejected
Rejected --> Delivered : submit
Delivered --> Closed : update
Delivered : entry / log fine
Closed --> Shipped : confirm
Shipped --> Archived : process
Rejected --> Closed : revert
Archived --> [*]
@enduml